{"tid":1275951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千祈，千祈，千祈，唔好，唔好，唔好同人講衝過立法會","createTime":"2019-07-02T00:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T04:51:18.000Z","uid":271829,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8228827a01d9aa9f5da456c30a2a7bb70dd7d0b4","tid":1275951,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:29:07.000Z","msg":"政府最鐘意玩秋後算帳，等幾個月以至幾年都一定等得，<br />\n等民意平息，搜夠證據就會上門拉人。<br />\n我知大家成日發夢入立法會一日遊，又或者思覺失調以為自己做過一日議員，<br />\n但無論點都會，就算係最親，都唔同佢講自己衝入過去，<br />\n口頭上唔好講，文字上諸如whatsapp，telegram就更加更加唔好。<br />\n香港嘅監獄係留俾共狗，你哋唔好霸咗佢哋個位<br />\n記住， 一個都嫌多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04feb2e5a723f09600c845f957ee04959e253d0f","tid":1275951,"uid":146917,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:33:21.000Z","msg":"得曬命先會講"},{"pid":"7b3fa98c09521322e0bc1722804a483c673db3fb","tid":1275951,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:33:29.000Z","msg":"發夢頭盔都唔夠厚"},{"pid":"3b3f17b68dd9698cf7c2b68b5be855ef0322a5d0","tid":1275951,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:37:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1dde9c7a14ad95ce98c8ee6106eb036a5f1827c","tid":1275951,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:10:55.000Z","msg":"德批難民庇護<br />\n黃台仰 李東昇：我們未必是最後兩人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190523/20685330\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190523%2F20685330&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9C8VJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=7bc2eace\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190523%2F20685330&h=896e7635\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190523/20685330</a>"},{"pid":"7ebd8bcb6416618ab341c105df25d5032484dea4","tid":1275951,"uid":264459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:51:18.000Z","msg":"求討論致勝一擊 後續行動<br />\n<br />\n我地一直圍政總警總佔路等等都係處於主動位<br />\n政府就可以完全被動 唔回應9回應都吹佢唔漲<br />\n唔知勇武仲可以升級到咩程度<br />\n好多人今個月以來次次出黎好攰 唔知可以撐到幾時<br />\n所以需要大家一齊brainstorm關鍵一擊<br />\n逼使致府落入主動位置同道德低地<br />\n實行以弱制強<br />\n<br />\n大家唔需要同意我提議既做法 純粹例子<br />\n只想拋磚引玉<br />\n隨便負皮 只求開放討論<br />\n<br />\n[緊急策略] 我地一直處於主動 任政府抹黑冷處理 係時候拋返舊屎比林鄭食了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1276622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1276622</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}